title: played ashe bot lane last game in normals........
body: soon as i get to lane corki and bard all in me and annie so we back off then nidalee comes throwing spears from behind the bush in our tower ok np we die we get back to lane im at about  5 cs now as ashe....... azir comes in diving level 4 with nidalee throwing more spears lol ok we pick up a triple and i die im now 0-2 with 5 cs. i get back to lane they do it again annie picks up a double i die im now 0-3 with 5 cs annie is 6-2 with most the farm lol. at this point im really annoyed and when i get back to lane this time nasus tps into the bush behind our tower and nidalee and azir come an 5 man dive me im now 0-4 with 5 cs....... annie picks up another 3 kills and my farm. and then i get back to lane and die again im fucking 0-5 now but annie bought ap items and conts to carry the game cause ashe hungry games ended up to fed annie.
